            "description": "As paleontologist Stephen Godfrey walked into the Calvert Marine Museum one morning in April, other staffers congratulated him. In a way, he had brought an extinct species back to life: His proposal to make a prehistoric shark the state's official shark is now law.",
            "summary": "",
